    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📋 Workflow Overview\n\n**Purpose:** Customer Feedback Collection & Discount Assignment\n\nThis workflow collects customer feedback through a form, automatically assigns discounts to customers who provide positive feedback, and logs all responses to a Google Sheet.\n\n**Flow:** Form → Check Feedback → Assign Discount → Save to Sheet",
        "height": 216,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "3b257546-eb83-4342-8e4c-2f8e024faa59",
      "name": "Sticky Note 0bc9f4ff",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1008,
        -560
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📝 Form Trigger\n\n**Collects 4 fields:**\n• Email ID (required)\n• Name (required)\n• Age (required)\n• Feedback dropdown: Positive, Neutral, or Negative\n\n**Output example:**\n```\n{\n  \"Email ID\": \"John@google.com\",\n  \"Name\": \"John,\n  \"Age\": 15,\n  \"Feedback\": \"Negative\",\n  \"submittedAt\": \"2026-05-18T09:53:08.125-04:00\"\n}\n```",
        "height": 424,
        "width": 412,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "828858d7-d807-4a48-b2a5-3bf8f8a9e3f9",
      "name": "Sticky Note 79650c08",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1136,
        16
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔀 Conditional Branching\n\n**Checks:** Is Feedback = \"Positive\"?\n\n**True branch:** Customer gets discount\n**False branch:** No discount (Neutral or Negative feedback)\n\nThis implements a reward system for positive customer feedback.",
        "height": 248,
        "width": 300,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "eafe57bc-3a9e-46f6-8a71-4ea34999b94b",
      "name": "Sticky Note d86751c1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -592,
        16
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 💰 Discount Assignment\n\n**Discount_yes:** Adds `Discount: \"Yes\"` field\n**Discount_No:** Adds `Discount: \"No\"` field\n\nBoth nodes preserve all original form data using `includeOtherFields: true`\n\n**Result:** Original data + new Discount field",
        "height": 216,
        "width": 316,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "02d3db06-6dfc-48fc-a7af-8d61f06d7a4e",
      "name": "Sticky Note 73cf1b50",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -192,
        192
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔗 Merge Node\n\n**Purpose:** Combines both branches back into one flow\n\n**Mode:** Append (concatenates all items from both inputs)\n\nThis ensures all form submissions—regardless of feedback type—proceed to the Google Sheet logging step.",
        "height": 216,
        "width": 332,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "18b6188b-1a63-412e-9986-4aeb999de665",
      "name": "Sticky Note ad4e024f",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        224,
        48
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📊 Google Sheets Logging\n\n**Action:** Appends each submission as a new row\n\n**Columns mapped:**\n• Email ID\n• Name\n• Age\n• Feedback\n• submittedAt\n• formMode\n• Discount (added by previous nodes)\n\n**Result:** Permanent record of all feedback with discount eligibility",
        "height": 360,
        "width": 300,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "484e1cd2-c3a8-495b-8d9c-08399a40463d",
      "name": "Sticky Note d5f4823c",
