      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ✨ Key Features\n\n1️⃣ **Automated Incentive:** Positive feedback = automatic discount\n2️⃣ **Complete Data Preservation:** All form fields retained throughout\n3️⃣ **Unified Logging:** Both discount and non-discount cases saved\n4️⃣ **Timestamp Tracking:** Submission time recorded\n5️⃣ **Scalable:** Handles multiple simultaneous submissions",
        "color": 4
